              <xs:element name="smoking_status" maxOccurs="1" minOccurs="0">
                <xs:annotation>
                  <xs:documentation>
                    This element is for selecting the current smoking status of the member (449868002 = Current every day smoker, 428041000124106 = Current some day smoker, 8517006 = Former smoker, 266919005 = Never smoker, 77176002 = Smoker - current status unknown, 266927001 = Unknown if ever smoked, 428071000124103 = Current Heavy tobacco smoker, 428061000124105 = Current Light tobacco smoker).  More information can be found here:  http://hl7.org/fhir/us/core/ValueSet-us-core-observation-smokingstatus.html
